title: Chanel Wallet On Chain Caviarskin Bag
description: Chanel Wallet On Chain bag in black diamond-quilted caviar leather (#JTxxxxxx: after year 2021). Featuring gold-toned hardware, rear exterior pocket, and CC logo on front flap. The snap button closure opens to an exterior patch pocket, a zipper pocket and a burgundy textile interior with card slots and a leather slip pocket. Approximate dimensions: 19cm(L) x 12cm(H) x 4cm(D), and 62cm leather-chain woven sliding shoulder strap drop. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
